# TOOLS.md

Which tools exist here and how to invoke them.

## MCP Gateway

Single URL: `http://mcp-gateway:8811/mcp` via `openclaw-mcp-bridge` plugin (server name: `gateway`).

Use `gateway__call` with `{"tool": "<inner_name>", "args": {...}}` or flat tools when they appear in context. Flat tool names follow the pattern `gateway__<server>__<tool>`.

## Search & Web

| Tool | When |
|------|------|
| `gateway__tavily__tavily_search` | General web search (primary) |
| `gateway__tavily__tavily_extract` | Extract content from a URL |
| `gateway__tavily__tavily_research` | Deep multi-query research |
| `gateway__duckduckgo__search` | Simple web search (backup) |
| `web_fetch` | Fetch raw HTML from a URL |

Built-in `browser` is denied. Built-in `web_search` is disabled. Use the tools above.

## ComfyUI

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `gateway__comfyui__list_workflows` | List available workflows |
| `gateway__comfyui__run_workflow` | Execute a workflow |
| `gateway__comfyui__list_comfyui_model_packs` | List downloadable model packs |
| `gateway__comfyui__pull_comfyui_models` | Download model packs |
| `gateway__comfyui__get_comfyui_model_pull_status` | Check pull progress |
| `gateway__comfyui__restart_comfyui` | Restart ComfyUI service |

Outputs: `GET http://dashboard:8080/api/orchestration/outputs` or MCP `list_outputs`.

Do **not** drive ComfyUI via `exec` + `curl` to `/prompt` - use MCP tools.

## n8n

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `gateway__n8n__list_workflows` | List n8n workflows |
| `gateway__n8n__execute_workflow` | Run a workflow |

Never create or modify n8n workflows from within OpenClaw.

## Orchestration

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `list_jobs` / `list_outputs` | Read job queue and results |
| `run_workflow` / `cancel_run` | Queue or cancel a job |
| `save_workflow` / `list_workflow_versions` | Workflow versioning |
| `create_schedule` / `update_schedule` / `delete_schedule` | Cron management |

## Core Services

| Service | URL | Auth |
|---------|-----|------|
| Model Gateway | `http://model-gateway:11435/v1` | Header: `X-Service-Name: openclaw` |
| MCP Gateway | `http://mcp-gateway:8811/mcp` | MCP protocol |
| Dashboard | `http://dashboard:8080` | Bearer: `DASHBOARD_AUTH_TOKEN` |
| ComfyUI | `http://comfyui:8188` | None (prefer MCP) |
| n8n | `http://n8n:5678` | MCP only |
| OpenClaw UI | `http://openclaw-gateway:6680` | Bearer token |

## Discord

`message` tool with `to: "channel:<snowflake>"`. Respect per-message size limits.

## Stack Ops

Service lifecycle, model pulls, self-healing: **`agents/stack-ops.md`**.
Compose, model downloads, MCP troubleshooting: **`agents/docker-ops.md`**.
